= Mix_SetSoundFonts =

Set SoundFonts paths to use by supported MIDI backends 

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int Mix_SetSoundFonts(const char *paths);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''paths'''
|paths
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 1 if successful, 0 on error

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL_mixer 2.0.0.

